{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fd599c698f","title":"苗春亭谈“遵义事件”(一)","origin":"张再兴编《1959-1960年“贵州事件”资料集》（贵阳，2002）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"668faaa22e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":2,"articleId":"fd599c698f"}],"tags":[{"id":"4f45e132a9","name":"贵州文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"133ade5f34","name":"贵州"},{"id":"5cf77c4641","name":"苗春亭"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"11c5cd040a","type":"title","text":"苗春亭谈“遵义事件”(一)","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"f0931ac46f","type":"authors","text":"贵州苗春亭","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"3fa2c033fc","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1967年元月2日","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e8581c26f7","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：贵州工学院学生宿舍5902，305室","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"0a5d1232f9","type":"paragraph","text":"被采访人：苗春亭(现任贵州省副省长，59年出现饿死人的事件时也任此职务)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"d436f4c836","type":"paragraph","text":"采访人：袁昌新、张再兴等","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e7049e8792","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“遵义事件”产生的原因是什么？你们为什么搞高估产、高征购？58年估产多少斤59年估产多少？60年估产多少斤？","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"67d484e016","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：58年估产120亿斤，59年估产130亿斤，60年估产60亿斤。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"224cdf5a0e","type":"paragraph","text":"问：60年的340亿是谁提出来的？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"ef115719c7","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：记不清了，这是个争取数字。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"4d8a3703f1","type":"paragraph","text":"问：各年的实际产量是多少？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"8d2d86cc80","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：58年是100多亿斤，59年是80多亿斤，60年是60亿斤。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"ab6fb19aeb","type":"paragraph","text":"问：各年的征购数字是多少？","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"bd35077788","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：58年大概是20多亿斤，59年也是20多亿斤，25-26亿斤，最高不过28亿斤，60年是20亿左右。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"72c8637149","type":"paragraph","text":"问：59年冬天，“五、五、二制”是谁提出来的(“五、五、二”是当时农村粮食指标，每人每天5两谷子(十六两制)、5两代食品、2斤菜)？","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c9484ee5e4","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：这个是省委，是周林提出来的。周林从四川回来，就推广这个。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"0caa4dceb5","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“富裕农民”是谁提出的？“论中农”是谁写的？","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"80e4aabe1b","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：59年提过，我也提过，“论中农”我不了解有这么回事。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"0a34068c9e","type":"paragraph","text":"问：到底什么叫富裕农民？你们是怎样划富裕农民的？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"384684601c","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：有的老的富裕农民，就是原来划的，有的新的上中农，主要搞的是些基层干部。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"d2dec96eaf","type":"paragraph","text":"问：58年分配粮食指标时，各专区不同意指标这样高，苗春亭曾打电话给周林，周林说：“有右倾思想在作怪”，后来苗春亭就强行分配任务，有没有这回事？","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"be0d4f3109","type":"paragraph","text":"苗；当时庐山会议上提出反右倾鼓干劲。周林回来，讲过反右倾的精神。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"b5ae07a5a6","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们分配的任务高还是低？","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e6d320b796","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：高。59年最高，征购任务最重。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"cbf45d2b8c","type":"paragraph","text":"问：反“常、夏、李反党集团”，是哪个干的？据说是你们的眼中钉？","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"3652629c20","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：反“常、夏、李反党集团”，是周林从庐山回来，认为他是右倾，那个时候常颂已经死了。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c42a375534","type":"paragraph","text":"问：是你们想借反右倾的名义反“常、夏、李”，还是搞些什么？","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"048a7d4fd0","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：事实有出入，打击面很宽，列举他们的事实有很大错误，性质也错了。这个事有个专案材料，64年“四清”平反有详细材料可查。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c391ce13f2","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们为什么要反“常、夏、李”？到底这些人错在哪里？","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"47dca14033","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：要追根，就在党内有不同意见，压制民主，主要是常颂同志有不同意见。58年在花溪开会说是常颂讲过，‘社会主义改造，条条鞭都打在农民身上’，后来又说不是那样讲的。依我看常颂比较深入实际。党内不民主嘛！长期形成隔阂。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"07490f12ee","type":"paragraph","text":"问：常颂曾经提出过一个文件，是怎么回事？","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"a174f1f647","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：省委那时开会，提出一个修改报告，后来常颂同志交给地委同志改了一下，可能有些夸大。省委认为是背着省委搞非法活动，根本焦点在于不民主。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c7482367ae","type":"paragraph","text":"问：59年国庆(注：应是59年初夏)，遵义发了1亿3千万斤粮食，被徐健生制止并批评了，对不对？","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"f7c58016ea","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：这我清楚。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e8ff944ecf","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“四清”揭发周林两件事，(1)说周林在湄潭看见人剐树皮时说：剐树皮就是剐我周林的脸皮，剐树皮就是有反革命捣乱；(2)说过谁开我的仓，就斩断谁的爪子？","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"a3c69984e2","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：他过热检查没有谈，可能说过谁开仓谁负责。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"a8f53c5ba7","type":"paragraph","text":"问：当时，不准动用交通沿线的粮食，只能到边远地区去调？","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"a17db78728","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：这个事实李书波最清楚，徐健生专管粮食，他当时到兴义去了。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"09e978db78","type":"paragraph","text":"问：当时规定旧历年前(59年)不供应粮食，是谁规定的？","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"10979f6552","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：大概是省委吧，那可能是我，有这个意思，粮食方面，周林、徐健生抓得多一些。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"4fdf53d9f5","type":"paragraph","text":"问：中央监委去过湄潭没有？赵欲樵去湄谈是在中央监委之前呢？还是在后面呢？","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c6a67ffa9f","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：中央监委去过湄潭，当时中央监委金兆典去的，比赵欲樵后去，赵欲樵先去。赵欲樵是60年春，大概3、4月间去的，中央监委是60年夏去的。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c330feeccf","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们怎样布置赵欲樵去的？","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"5d693ccbe1","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：是说赵欲樵去救灾。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"34724d8b78","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们没有布置其他？","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"85b47ea079","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：没有，我个人保证没有布置。省委开会让赵欲樵是去对李书波帮助他工作。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e4b9a02926","type":"paragraph","text":"问：帮助干什么？","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"f8ace6ea78","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：说是帮他搞工作。周林说过只能吃补药，不能吃泻药，要央到搞。赵欲樵去的时候，周林跟他个人谈过。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"b950384a09","type":"paragraph","text":"问：什么叫吃补药、吃泻药，什么叫“央到搞”？","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"846519d976","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：就是取消斗争，搞阶级调和。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"f44be9ae85","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们是否布置赵欲樵控制遵义，欺骗中央监委？","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"095e50c6cb","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：赵欲樵是去帮助工作的，中央监委后来来了时候，他们才对口径(在遵义宾馆)。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"b8c2fef25a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“遵义事件”是由专区负责呢还是由省委负责？","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"a386d4aac1","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：由省委负责，(专区)负责错了。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"6ad26e26b2","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们为何往下推？","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"f704932ef2","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：64年我检讨了，我们没有自我表现革命精神，没有追到省委来。可是那个时候分析死了那么多人，怕干部搞乱了，因而央到搞。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"3422487ed4","type":"paragraph","text":"问：59年灾情这么严重，你们省委是什么时候发现的？","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"6524e77857","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：吴实在三合市、桐梓，大概是59年春节发现的。","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"206d6db164","type":"paragraph","text":"问：在这以前，你们知道吗？","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"43df1d541e","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：在以前，知道有些地方粮食紧张，那时以为是少数地方。","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"37302dee47","type":"paragraph","text":"问：各个专区给你们反映过多少次情况？","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"4a2b9019fd","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：我听徐健生讲过，我不知道，在吴实发现以后，他们开会谈过这个情况，以前汇报很少。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"2d10cc0e8e","type":"paragraph","text":"问：当时下面反映指标高了，交不了粮，你们怎么对待的？","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"4b1b5a0c8d","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：我们对灾情估计不足，当时决定处理半斤粮，决定带着粮食下乡。","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"cecf0b5714","type":"paragraph","text":"问：当时你们搞食堂现场展览，听说当场就死了3人？中央发给粮食你要了没有？","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e1b6a4a87d","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：我们没有要粮。我没听说当场死人，我听说知道是后来死人的。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c02e88ba4e","type":"paragraph","text":"问：《党内通信》六条下来以后，你们怎样对待？怎样贯彻执行的？","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"ede1c98893","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：按照规定发下了的。那个时候我们头脑也发热，讲了栽秧一亩要栽多少窝呀，怕农民动摇了。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e3cc03b0fb","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们采取了哪些措施？","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"21c7ea41ac","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：没有采取措施，就规定了生产指标，规定了一亩要栽多少窝。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e989352391","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你们后来搞了八条，来对抗主席指示，你们说“六条是主席回韶山，听了群众意见，写这封信是应付群众的，不能全信”，说过了没有？","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"d8e8fec9e8","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：没有说过，不会这样说的，这样太露骨了嘛！","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"783419aebc","type":"paragraph","text":"问：庐山会议前一段，有个19条指示，周林回来后传达过没有？","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"328437f607","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：这个没有传达，没有个文字的19条。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"46eede2947","type":"paragraph","text":"问：中央关于一平二调，有个十二条，你得到了吗？","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"d02f64c9b3","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：得到了的，是59年春传达，反一平二调三收款。先开了大会，接着整风整社，整顿人民公社的体制。二调是把农民的生产资料往社里调，一平是贫富平均，大家一样，三收款是银行扣钱，当时我们纠正了这个。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"2e8a56fc41","type":"paragraph","text":"问：那么，牵牛拉马又是怎么搞的？你为什么在这个问题上大做文章？借口反牵牛拉马抵制反一平二调？","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"e25ac3160a","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：反牵牛拉马是以后，是少数人，有个别人想把社里的东西拉走，反牵牛拉马是庐山会议以后根据反右倾的精神干的。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"475bdf6929","type":"paragraph","text":"问：中央曾拨钱赔款，拨钱赔款的指标是多少，你们什么不退赔？","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c90b894e02","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：拨了几次，开始拨得少，拨了几千万。","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c25625730c","type":"appellation","text":"问：中央关于人民公社体制是怎样提的？","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"dd4921b5c3","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：有一个文件，是集体所有制逐步向全民所有制过渡。59年确实以大队为基本核算单位，59年春，由公社所有制改为集体所有制。","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"8d3084ef26","type":"paragraph","text":"问：粮食、工资供给制是谁提出来的？","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"0017cad879","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：我们也这样提，全国都是这样的。","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"d0965fa7a3","type":"paragraph","text":"问：当时吃饭不要钱是谁提出来的？","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"291bba5187","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：吃饭不要钱是我提出来的。","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"93c23fecf0","type":"paragraph","text":"问：当时纠正单干，中央有文件，省委的态度如何？","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"47efe35c73","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：当时没有，省委发了个文件，中心区要坚决纠，边远地区纠不了也不要勉强纠，中央没有指示(指61、62年)。","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"96e0b4b3e9","type":"paragraph","text":"问：为什么中心区你们就要坚决纠，边远地区纠不了就算？","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"fd06afc83d","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：中心区人口集中，条件好，能纠正得好，边远地区基础差，我们纠得不坚决。","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"c15760be9a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：还有其他一些问题，如汪小川的“二铺调查”，是不是按周林的意见写的？大方调查是谁写的？","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"1de628f0c7","type":"paragraph","text":"苗：“二铺调查”是汪小川自己写的。大方调查我们不知道，汪小川到桐梓去的。","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"},{"id":"4e554f6095","type":"paragraph","text":"会议到此结束，散会。","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f"}],"page":{"id":"0bfb4239d1","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fd599c698f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}